{"id":186669,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/厦门出租车罢工-晚上越闹越凶-见车就砸见人就打-40/","date":"2011-10-07T01:00:07Z","modified":"2011-10-07T01:07:37Z","title":"厦门出租车罢工 (40多图)","content":"<p><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<div><span><span>2011</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>6</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日厦门的士罢工的起因是出租车的承包价格过高，每月除去承包费用后收入所得不足</span><span>1000</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">元，许多司机都怨声载道，多次和车主公司反映都得不到解决，于是他们才发起这次行动。</span><span></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日前所有厦门的士收到通知，</span><span>10</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>6</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日开始罢工，要把车停在家里，出车者后果自负。</span><span></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>10</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>6</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日早上，大批的哥聚集在会展中心前十字路口与警察对峙，造成交通大堵塞。到晚上，的哥情绪更加激动，见车就砸，见人就打，被砸的出租车不下</span><span>60</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">部。当局出动公安武警上千人维稳。</span><span></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><strong><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">相关连接：<span><a href=\"http://www.molihua.org/2011/10/20_06.html\">【首发】厦门出租车大罢工</a></span></span><span> (20</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">图</span><span>)</span></span><span> </span></span></span></strong></span></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-glAWcZxHDdg/To3-b8nHy7I/AAAAAAAADYc/jFXoNcsvRQU/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-glAWcZxHDdg/To3-b8nHy7I/AAAAAAAADYc/jFXoNcsvRQU/s1600/1.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sceOcgFD2Xc/To3-chOQznI/AAAAAAAADYg/6RbVtoKEC_Y/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-sceOcgFD2Xc/To3-chOQznI/AAAAAAAADYg/6RbVtoKEC_Y/s1600/2.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6np7RdFGTAs/To3-dVCSCmI/AAAAAAAADYk/7wGDAyEBqjw/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-6np7RdFGTAs/To3-dVCSCmI/AAAAAAAADYk/7wGDAyEBqjw/s1600/3.jpg